OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FN America uniforms linked  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto "forever chemicals"     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A study of school uniforms in the US   
OL,6, and Canada reveals high levels of      
OL,7, so-called "forever chemicals".         
OL,9,FThe chemicals, known as PFAS, are used 
OL,10,Fto make clothing resistant to stains or
OL,11,Fwater but they have been linked to     
OL,12,Fasthma, obesity and fertility issues.  
OL,14,FResearchers found that uniforms made   
OL,15,Fwith 100% cotton showed higher levels  
OL,16,Fthan synthetic materials.              
OL,18,FExposing children to these chemicals   
OL,19,Fmay increase the long-term health risk,
OL,20,Fthe scientists believe.                
